Would you like to purchase this home?
*****************************************
------------------MAKE ME AN OFFER!----------------------

WOULD YOU LIKE THIS TRULY  LIVABLE HOME IN A SPECTACULAR WILDERNESS AREA? ------ A ONE FLOOR HOME THAT IS AN EXTREMELY LOW PRICE FOR ITS QUALITY CONSTRUCTION AND FEATURES. IT HAS NO COMPARABLE PROPERTIES TO IT IN ALL NORTH WEST MONTANA.
----------------------------------------------------------------
A ONE FLOOR HOME IS MUCH MORE EXPENSIVE TO CONSTRUCT THAN A MULTI - FLOOR HOME.
-------------------------------------------------------------------
---------if you would love owning this home ----------
-------------------make me an offer! -------------------------

ARE THESE EXTRAORDINARY FEATURES  AND CONSTRUCTION AND LOCATION FOR THIS ONE FLOOR HOME AT SUCH VERY LOW PRICE IS APPEALING TO YOU? 

CALL OR EMAIL FOR A VISIT OR OBTAIN A  PERSONAL BUILDING INSPECTOR TO VERIFY THE VALUE AND AMBIANCE OF THIS RESIDENCE.

THERE ARE NO COMPARABLE RESIDENCES AVAILABLE FOR SALE IN ALL OF N. W. MONTANA.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------- 
Call Owner: Ed Bowling (406)293-3597
or Email: edbowling1@outlook.com.
--------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------
DISCERNING INTERESTED BUYERS WHO WOULD ENJOY THIS HOME WILL QUICKLY AND EASILY RECOGNIZE ITS UNIQUE QUALITIES, VALUES AND CLOSE TO EVERYTHING CONVENIENT LOCATION. ITS LIVABILITY AND PRICE ARE INCOMPARABLE. IF YOU COMPARE THIS HOME TO ALL OTHER HOMES WITH ONE FLOOR WITHOUT ANY STEPS IN ANY AREA OF NORTHWEST MONTANA THAT ARE CURRENTLY ON THE MARKET OR THAT HAVE BEEN SOLD, YOU WILL BE DELIGHTED WITH YOUR CHOICE. 
ITS LIKE LIVING IN A LITTLE SWITZERLAND RIGHT HERE IN AMERICA. THIS HOME IS ALSO SITUATED IN ONE OF THE MOST COVETED PROPERTY LOCATIONS IN THE COUNTY. IT'S SITUATED TO BE CLOSE TO EVERYTHING, WILDERNESS AREAS: HIKING, SWIMMING, CANNONING, BOATING WITH MOST EVERY SIZE OF BOATS, CAMPING, HUNTING, FISHING IN SMALL STREAMS TO THE BEAUTIFUL KOOTENAI RIVER, A MYRIAD OF WILD LIFE, EXTRA GOOD HOME STYLE COOKING RESTAURANTS, A LARGE BREWERY WITH GREAT FOOD, AN EXCELLENT FOOD MARKET, A NEW HOSPITAL, FRIENDLY PEOPLE, THEATER, MOST CHURCH DENOMINATIONS, IT'S JUST A WONDERFUL TOWN AND HOME TO LIVE IN!
---------------------------------------------------------------
THIS COMMUNITY HAS ALL THE SMALL TOWN LIVING ATTRIBUTES!  IF YOU WOULD LIKE THIS HEALTHFUL, QUIET, FRIENDLY, SAFE STYLE OF LIVING, ITS A MUST FOR YOU TO CONSIDER.
---------------------------------------------------------------
We decided to make this healthful wonderful small town and wilderness area our permanent residence. So, what we desired in this home was important to have built regardless of the costs. That is the reason it was constructed to have such a pleasant room arrangement, special features and to be an easily maintained home. You can see these qualities in the photographs. Even though a single floor home is more expensive, HAVING NO STEPS IS CERTAINLY A GREAT ADVANTAGE.
----------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------REASON FOR SELLING--------------------      
Situations beyond our control have arisen that we must move to a specialized assisted living facility in another state close to family members.
--------------------------------------------------------------------- 

-----------------------------------------------------------------
  Our location is of the most desired, close to everything properties in the Kootenai Valley hill side areas. It is also an affluent economically stable division with very little turn over of real estate. The neighborhood is safe for children and pets. The school bus will stop right at the drive way. This home is located on the premier parcel in this coveted one acre property division.
data.whatILove:
There are 3 & 1/2 bathrooms - a master bedroom, and 2 more bedrooms, a den you wouldn't believe until you see it & sitting room, kitchen, dining room, living room and sitting room. The office can easily be converted for another purpose. Living room & sitting room each with it's own fireplace. The huge family room has a complete bathroom, a full kitchen of its own and entrance. The three car garage is completely insulated, finished, heated, spacious work areas multiple storage and bathroom. Heating is the safest, non-allergenic, Cove heating system with no air movement, automatically controlled as desired in each room. Installed in the corner of the wall and ceiling, furniture and pictures can be placed any place desired. There are two large walk in storage areas conveniently situated. Paved U shaped driveway also has ample off-street parking for additional guests. All landscaping is automatically irrigated and controlled inside the house. Water is sweet. The gallons per hour and pressure are high for household use and the extensive irrigation system. Electrical system is 440 Volts. Its within minutes of hiking, giant fresh running water swimming pool, Cabinet Mountain Range with numerous creeks and lakes. Fishing, hunting, world renown canoeing, rafting, boating, down hill skiing slope, cross country skiing, snow snowmobiling and many ATV trails, and many, many miles of Forest Service maintained hiking trails. Abundant wildlife include most species of wild animals in the U.S and a myriad of species of all types of bird life can be seen. The 60 mile long, LAKE KOOCANUSCA, hosts most every water sport. Marinas are large enough to launch large sized boats. Swimming is also at its best in the ONE-Of-ITS-KIND VERY LARGE FRESH WATER SWIMMING POOL that IS INCLUDED IN THE PICTURES. 
IMPORTANT: county - snow plows the streets in this area as often as needed because it is a school bus street. The bus will pickup and return your children right in front of your home!
